---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Web Development in 2026: What Local Businesses Need to Know"
  description="Stay ahead of the curve with our guide on the state of web development in 2026. Learn about AI, mobile-only design, and security for local Shelby businesses."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-cyan/20 bg-brand-cyan/5">
          <span class="text-brand-cyan text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #2 Article #8</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">May 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          Web Development in 2026: <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-blue">What Your Business Needs to Know</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          The landscape of web development continues to evolve rapidly. Here's what local businesses need to understand about building and maintaining a competitive online presence in 2026.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12">Shelby Web Company Official</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">01.</span> The State of Web Development in 2026
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/90 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Web development has transformed dramatically over the past few years. What was once about simply having a website has evolved into creating comprehensive digital experiences that drive business growth. For local businesses—home service experts, service providers, and small retailers—understanding these changes is crucial for staying competitive.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/90 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          In 2026, web development isn't just about code. It's about creating fast, accessible, and user-friendly experiences that convert visitors into customers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">02.</span> Key Trends Shaping 2026
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AI-Powered Development</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Artificial intelligence has revolutionized coding and optimization. For local businesses, this means higher-quality websites at more competitive prices.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Mobile-Only Era</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Successful websites are now built with mobile users as the primary audience. Touch-friendly interfaces and lightning-fast mobile speeds are non-negotiable.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Security by Default</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">With increasing threats, modern development prioritizes security from the ground up—not as an afterthought.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Performance Ranking</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Google's Core Web Vitals make performance a critical SEO factor. Minimized bloat and smooth interactions are essential for ranking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-blue/5 border-l-4 border-brand-blue p-8 my-12 rounded-r-2xl">
          <p class="text-white font-medium italic mb-0">"At Shelby Web Company, we specialize in helping local businesses navigate the complexities of modern web development. We combine cutting-edge technology with local market understanding."</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">03.</span> What This Means for Your Business
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">For local businesses, these trends translate into concrete requirements for your online presence:</p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-6 list-none p-0 mb-16">
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/10 border border-brand-cyan/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-cyan font-bold text-sm">✓</div>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 m-0">Fast loading websites that perform well on mobile devices</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/10 border border-brand-cyan/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-cyan font-bold text-sm">✓</div>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 m-0">Secure payment processing and customer data protection</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/10 border border-brand-cyan/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-cyan font-bold text-sm">✓</div>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 m-0">Local SEO optimization for Google Business Profile results</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/10 border border-brand-cyan/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-cyan font-bold text-sm">✓</div>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 m-0">Integration with booking systems and CRM software</p>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-dark p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(132,204,22,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10">Ready to Modernize Your Web Presence?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Let's discuss how modern web development can help your local business grow in 2026.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-glow-shine bg-brand-accent text-[#0A0A0A] px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-accent-light">
              Free Consultation
            </a>
            <a href="tel:7044738188" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
              (704) 473-8188
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-8 relative z-10">
            Visit <a href="/" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white underline underline-offset-4">www.shelbywebco.com</a> to view our work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Web Design</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
